  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.poster.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.webm?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.mp4?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an epic battle to save Earth from an alien invasion in Tilebreaker Next Level! The aliens have encased the planet in a network of dark, impenetrable blocks, and it's up to you to shatter them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.poster.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.webm?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.mp4?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself and prepare for fast-paced action, dodging deadly enemy attacks and facing off against formidable alien bosses in heart-pumping battles. As you progress through increasingly challenging levels, you'll encounter complex attack patterns, tougher blocks, and unexpected obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.poster.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.webm?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.mp4?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with players worldwide to achieve the fastest completion times and climb the ranks. Can you break into the top 5?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/406be1db32c9fa9d0e48ee02775f8a95.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won't be fighting alone, though! Take control of your powerful hero and keep an eye out for valuable power-ups, such as increased speed, damage, and more. With quick reflexes and strategic thinking, you'll overcome the most daunting challenges and move closer to your ultimate goal: destroying the source of the blocks and restoring light to Earth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/7f08147fe5073ab3e89024f2ae916187.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are you ready to join the fight, save the planet, and experience non-stop action? Let's play Tilebreaker Next Level!</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.poster.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.webm?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/27fb2ed6423fe72d296904132b66a963.mp4?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an epic battle to save Earth from an alien invasion in Tilebreaker Next Level! The aliens have encased the planet in a network of dark, impenetrable blocks, and it's up to you to shatter them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.poster.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.webm?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/89ce2a9d8b92c5f494d2da20d728ea42.mp4?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself and prepare for fast-paced action, dodging deadly enemy attacks and facing off against formidable alien bosses in heart-pumping battles. As you progress through increasingly challenging levels, you'll encounter complex attack patterns, tougher blocks, and unexpected obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.poster.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.webm?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/af7ae5260bf88c84a417d1abbd396759.mp4?t=1740746693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with players worldwide to achieve the fastest completion times and climb the ranks. Can you break into the top 5?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/406be1db32c9fa9d0e48ee02775f8a95.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won't be fighting alone, though! Take control of your powerful hero and keep an eye out for valuable power-ups, such as increased speed, damage, and more. With quick reflexes and strategic thinking, you'll overcome the most daunting challenges and move closer to your ultimate goal: destroying the source of the blocks and restoring light to Earth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162340/extras/7f08147fe5073ab3e89024f2ae916187.avif?t=1740746693\" width=610 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are you ready to join the fight, save the planet, and experience non-stop action? Let's play Tilebreaker Next Level!</strong></h2>",
